1. create the database as instructed in the file DATABASE:
CREATE DATABASE intersango;
USE intersango;
...

2. modify config.php with your credentials for btc and mysql

3.
cd /var
sudo rm -fr www
ln -s /path/to/this/dir/www www

4. enable MySQL logging in /etc/mysql/my.cnf:
log = /var/log/mysql/mysql.log

5. import DATABASE into mysql

6. edit crontab -e, mark /var/tmp/error-reports.log as rw for users
